Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabijem ťa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,za to, čo si im urobil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To je ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Poď ma zabiť,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa-kun!
